      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver verified against analytical or manufactured solutions for relevant flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "Code verification confirmed via method of manufactured solutions for incompressible Navier-Stokes equations. Spatial and temporal order of accuracy confirmed at expected theoretical rates. Gradation 2 requirement satisfied."
