      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions documented and traceable; boundary conditions match CFD inlet/outlet specifications.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental dataset documents flow rates, rotational speeds, and fluid properties. CFD boundary conditions derived directly from published test protocols. Temperature and viscosity matched within 1% of experimental values. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
